<sect1 id="CleanAccents">
  <title>CleanAccents</title>

  <para><emphasis role="bold">STD.Uni.CleanAccents<indexterm>
      <primary>STD.Uni.CleanAccents</primary>
    </indexterm><indexterm>
      <primary>Uni.CleanAccents</primary>
    </indexterm><indexterm>
      <primary>CleanAccents</primary>
    </indexterm>(</emphasis> <emphasis>source</emphasis> <emphasis
  role="bold">)</emphasis></para>

  <informaltable colsep="1" frame="all" rowsep="1">
    <tgroup cols="2">
      <colspec colwidth="80.50pt"/>

      <colspec/>

      <tbody>
        <row>
          <entry><emphasis>source</emphasis></entry>

          <entry>Uma string que contém os dados a serem higienizados.</entry>
        </row>

        <row>
          <entry>Return:</entry>

          <entry>CleanAccents retorna um valor UNICODE.</entry>
        </row>
      </tbody>
    </tgroup>
  </informaltable>

  <para>A função <emphasis role="bold">CleanAccents </emphasis> retorna a
  string <emphasis>source</emphasis> com todos os caracteres acentuados
  substituídos pelos não acentuados.</para>

  <para>Exemplo:</para>

  <programlisting format="linespecific">UNICODE A := STD.Uni.CleanAccents(u'caf\u00E9');   //café - U+00E9 is lowercase e with acute
                                                   //a contains 'cafe'
</programlisting>

  <para/>
</sect1>
